# 🔒 SyqueX — Pre-Production Security Audit

> **Auditor:** Cybersecurity Audit (automated) · **Date:** 2026-04-16  
> **Scope:** Backend (FastAPI + PostgreSQL + Anthropic) + Frontend (React SPA)  
> **Standard:** OWASP Top 10 2021 + LFPDPPP (México)  
> **Classification:** Internal Engineering — CONFIDENTIAL

---

## Executive Summary

| Severity | Count | Status |
|---|---|---|
| 🔴 **CRITICAL** | 5 | Must fix before ANY deploy |
| 🟠 **HIGH** | 7 | Must fix before production |
| 🟡 **MEDIUM** | 6 | Fix scheduled within sprint 1 |
| 🔵 **LOW** | 5 | Recommended hardening |
| **Total** | **23** | |

> [!CAUTION]
> **5 CRITICAL vulnerabilities were found.** Do NOT deploy to production until all CRITICAL and HIGH items are resolved. Two findings (CRIT-01 and CRIT-02) represent immediate data breach risks under LFPDPPP.

