## ✅ What's Already Done Well

| Area | Implementation | Grade |
|---|---|---|
| **Password Hashing** | bcrypt 12 rounds via passlib ✅ | A |
| **JWT Architecture** | Access (30min) + Refresh (7d, httpOnly, Secure, SameSite=strict) ✅ | A |
| **Refresh Token Rotation** | SHA-256 hash storage + stolen token detection ✅ | A |
| **Token Storage (Frontend)** | In-memory only, never localStorage ✅ | A |
| **Refresh Race Condition** | Queue-based dedup in auth.js ✅ | A |
| **Brute-Force Protection** | 5 attempts / 15 min window ✅ | B+ (in-memory) |
| **Prompt Injection Guard** | Regex blocklist + input truncation ✅ | B+ |
| **Timing Attack Prevention** | Constant-time login + forgot-password delay ✅ | A |
| **Error Handling** | Global handler, no stack traces to client ✅ | A |
| **Security Headers** | X-Frame-Options, X-XSS, Referrer-Policy ✅ | B (missing CSP) |
| **Local Embeddings** | FastEmbed — no PII egress for vectors ✅ | A+ |
| **Audit Logging** | Immutable INSERT-only table, no PII in logs ✅ | A |
| **API Docs in Prod** | Disabled via `docs_url=None` ✅ | A |
| **Domain Error Hierarchy** | Clean error codes, no internal leaks ✅ | A |
| **UUIDs everywhere** | No sequential IDs on clinical entities ✅ | A |

